        "description": "*Includes the free Two-Handed, Old Mine, and Undead Valley updates!*\n\nVR meets the zombie apocalypse! Arizona Sunshine® is a shooter built exclusively for VR that immerses you in a southwestern America overrun by zombies. \n\nWhen you hear a flash of a human voice on the radio, your hopes surge - there are survivors out in the blistering heat of the post-apocalyptic Grand Canyon state! Armed with your motion-controlled weapons and the scarce ammo and consumables you find along the way, you need to navigate hordes of zombies coming for your brain in your desperate search for human contact.\n\n• Handle, fire, and reload over 25 different weapons with real-life movements\n• Explore huge environments including deserts, canyons, and mines\n• Full-size campaign\n• Co-op multiplayer: Join a friend in campaign mode or Horde mode (up to 4 players on Oculus Quest)",
